<div class="container-fluid text-center bg-grey" id="header">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col">
			<%= image_tag("Apocrypharius-A-orange.png", height: 150, alt: "Apocrypharius letter A" ) %>
			<h2 class="title" style="color: var(--purple);">site for research on manuscripts of<br>Christian apocrypha and parabiblica</h2>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="w-100 bg-blue pb-5" id="research">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 class="static-page text-center pt-5 mb-3" style="color: var(--grey)">Start research here</h1>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-4">
				<div class="card m-2">
					<div class="card-body px-4">
						<h3 class="static-page text-center">Apocrypha in manuscript</h3>
						<p>Use this grid to explore (whenever available)</p>
						<ul>
							<li>a census of manuscripts that preserve each apocryphal/parabiblical text</li>
							<li>brief descriptions of manuscript’s including their contents</li>
							<li>manuscripts’ origins and provenances</li>
							<li>titles, incipits, explicits, and colophons of each apocryphal / parabiblical text as they appear in manuscripts</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="text-center"><button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-action w-100" onclick="location.href='<%= sections_path %>'">Apocrypha in manuscript</button></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-4">
				<div class="card m-2">
					<div class="card-body px-4">
						<h3 class="static-page text-center">Apocrypha in booklists</h3>
						<p>Use this grid to explore (whenever available)</p>
						<ul>
							<li>a census of booklists that mention each apocryphal/parabiblical text</li>
							<li>brief identifications of booklists</li>
							<li>identifications of the books’ owner(s) and/or locations</li>
							<li>excerpts from booklists that mention an apocryphal/parabiblical text</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="text-center"><button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-action w-100" onclick="location.href='<%= booklist_sections_path %>'">Apocrypha in booklists</button></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-4">
				<div class="card m-2">
					<div class="card-body px-4">
						<h3 class="static-page text-center">A list of apocrypha</h3>
						<p>Use this grid to access</p>
						<ul>
							<li>a complete listing of apocryphal/parabibllical  texts surveyed on this website</li>
							<li>brief identifications of each text (CANT, BHL, BHG, e-Clavis)</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Please note: titles preceded by * are derived from booklists and cannot be fully identified</p>
						<p class="text-center"><button type="button" class="btn btn-lg btn-action w-100" onclick="location.href='<%= apocrypha_path %>'">A list of apocrypha</button></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
